{"tid":720711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國智庫警告可能現金融恐慌   報告上線3天被消失","createTime":"2018-06-28T06:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T08:53:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"55de822700a559d237428f3ef5b15e1fdf704660","tid":720711,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:42:19.000Z","msg":"中國經濟發展快速，但也潛藏不少問題，有中國智庫發布報告指出，中國極有可能出現金融恐慌。有趣的是，該報告曾短暫發表在網路上，但後來被撤下。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導，中國智庫「國家金融與發展實驗室」週一在網路上發表報告，報告顯示，今年以來，中國債券市場違約事件不斷、股市下挫，加上美國升息、美中貿易戰等不確定性因素，導致金融市場神經緊繃，極有可能出現金融恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，該報告建議，中國應立即啟動相應機構，並防範外部衝擊。然而這篇文章於週三，已在網站上消失。報導表示，智庫官員稱報告是用於內部討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2471632\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2471632&d=F9d%2FgIgD8apEe27ZTW%2FZcMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=ae5c1783\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2471632&h=4dbfac4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2471632</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12204488f67309da2171d42d26d0e5b49e88961a","tid":720711,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:44:42.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41467ea6ad7e382e1b91404d12567b02a5529001","tid":720711,"uid":116289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f98ae6f03cbc8b2757dbd537d1ec1ad65ba69ac","tid":720711,"uid":44454,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:47:32.000Z","msg":"金融恐慌已經解決了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1944c067684107820b05bef233657afeb36dc9be","tid":720711,"uid":184679,"like":1